          <li><span class="text-brand-cta dark:text-brand-cta-dark font-bold">✔</span> Order/Table Management</li>
          <li><span class="text-brand-cta dark:text-brand-cta-dark font-bold">✔</span> Full Inventory Management</li>
          <li><span class="text-brand-cta dark:text-brand-cta-dark font-bold">✔</span> All Reports (Item, Category, Employee)</li>
          <li><span class="text-brand-cta dark:text-brand-cta-dark font-bold">✔</span> Priority Email & Chat Support</li>
